== 評價 ==
《美女與野獸》廣受媒體和影評家的好評，[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度94%，基於118條評論，平均分為8.5/10<ref>{{cite web |title=Beauty and the Beast (1991 film)|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/beauty_and_the_beast_1991|website=[[爛番茄|爛番茄]] |publisher=Fandango Media |accessdate=2022-05-15}}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上根據22條評論，得到95分（滿分100分）<ref>{{cite web |title=Beauty and the Beast (1991 film)|url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/beauty-and-the-beast-1991|website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |publisher=|accessdate=2022-05-15}}</ref>，截至2022年5月15日，名列該網站影史百大動畫電影第6名<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.metacritic.com/browse/movies/genre/metascore/animation|script-title=en:Movie Releases by Genre|website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2022-05-15|archive-date=2022-05-15|archive-url=https://www.metacritic.com/browse/movies/genre/metascore/animation|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[影院評分|影院評分]]調查觀眾評級獲得「A+」的罕見高度評價<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/why-cinemascore-matters-box-office-225563|title=Why CinemaScore Matters for Box Office|author=Pamela McClintock|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=August 19, 2011|access-date=September 14, 2016|archive-date=April 26, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140426043610/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/why-cinemascore-matters-box-office-225563|url-status=live}}</ref>。


